          <p class="when">Use from the Draft app to merge engine baselines with MLB player bios. Same <code>x-api-key</code> as other Brain routes. Cached 120s per body hash when Redis is available. Higher default rate ceiling than valuation; still tunable via <code>RATE_LIMIT_CATALOG_*</code>.</p>
